## API Reference

### Auth

| Method | Endpoint                            | Auth   | Description             |
| ------ | ----------------------------------- | ------ | ----------------------- |
| POST   | `/api/v1/auth/register`             | —      | Register new user       |
| POST   | `/api/v1/auth/verify-email`         | —      | Verify email with OTP   |
| POST   | `/api/v1/auth/resend-otp`           | —      | Resend verification OTP |
| POST   | `/api/v1/auth/login`                | —      | Login                   |
| GET    | `/api/v1/auth/google`               | —      | Redirect to Google      |
| GET    | `/api/v1/auth/google/callback`      | —      | Google OAuth callback   |
| POST   | `/api/v1/auth/forget-password`      | —      | Send password reset OTP |
| POST   | `/api/v1/auth/reset-password`       | —      | Reset password with OTP |
| PATCH  | `/api/v1/auth/change-password`      | —      | Change password         |
| PATCH  | `/api/v1/auth/change-profile-image` | —      | Upload profile photo    |
| DELETE | `/api/v1/auth/users/:id`            | Admin  | Delete user             |
| GET    | `/api/v1/auth/refresh`              | Cookie | Refresh access token    |
| GET    | `/api/v1/auth/logout`               | —      | Logout                  |

### Providers

| Method | Endpoint                               | Auth     | Description             |
| ------ | -------------------------------------- | -------- | ----------------------- |
| POST   | `/api/v1/providers`                    | Provider | Create provider profile |
| GET    | `/api/v1/providers/:id`                | —        | Get provider by ID      |
| PATCH  | `/api/v1/providers/:id`                | Provider | Update provider         |
| POST   | `/api/v1/providers/:id/slots/generate` | Provider | Generate time slots     |

### Slots

| Method | Endpoint                          | Auth | Description                        |
| ------ | --------------------------------- | ---- | ---------------------------------- |
| GET    | `/api/v1/slots?providerId=&date=` | —    | Get slots for a provider on a date |
| GET    | `/api/v1/slots/:id`               | —    | Get slot by ID                     |

### Bookings

| Method | Endpoint                       | Auth  | Description     |
| ------ | ------------------------------ | ----- | --------------- |
| POST   | `/api/v1/bookings`             | User  | Book a slot     |
| GET    | `/api/v1/bookings/me`          | —     | My bookings     |
| PATCH  | `/api/v1/bookings/:id/confirm` | User  | Confirm booking |
| DELETE | `/api/v1/bookings/:id`         | User  | Cancel booking  |
| GET    | `/api/v1/bookings`             | Admin | All bookings    |

### Queue

| Method | Endpoint                         | Auth | Description        |
| ------ | -------------------------------- | ---- | ------------------ |
| POST   | `/api/v1/queue/:slotId/join`     | User | Join waitlist      |
| POST   | `/api/v1/queue/:slotId/confirm`  | User | Confirm queue slot |
| GET    | `/api/v1/queue/:slotId/position` | —    | My queue position  |
| DELETE | `/api/v1/queue/:slotId/leave`    | User | Leave queue        |

---

## Booking Flow

```
POST /bookings          → Lua atomic decrement (Redis)
                        → MongoDB transaction (booked++)
                        → BullMQ delay job (expires in N minutes)

BullMQ expiry job       → Mark EXPIRED + decrement booked
                        → Release Redis counter
                        → Promote next in queue
```

## Queue Flow

```
POST /queue/:id/join    → Add to Redis sorted set (ZADD score=timestamp)
                        → Create QueueEntry (WAITING)

Slot freed              → promoteBatch() → ZPOPMIN
                        → Mark NOTIFIED + set confirmationDeadline
                        → BullMQ delay job (confirm window)

POST /queue/:id/confirm → Lua atomic decrement
                        → Create Booking (CONFIRMED)
                        → Mark QueueEntry (CONFIRMED)

BullMQ confirm expiry   → Mark QueueEntry (EXPIRED)
                        → Promote next
```

---

## WebSocket Events

Connect with `auth: { token: '<accessToken>' }`.

| Event               | Direction       | Payload                               |
| ------------------- | --------------- | ------------------------------------- |
| `booking:created`   | Server → Client | `{ bookingId, slotId }`               |
| `booking:cancelled` | Server → Client | `{ bookingId, slotId }`               |
| `queue:joined`      | Server → Client | `{ slotId, position, estimatedWait }` |
| `queue:your_turn`   | Server → Client | `{ slotId, confirmationDeadline }`    |
| `queue:confirmed`   | Server → Client | `{ slotId }`                          |
| `queue:left`        | Server → Client | `{ slotId }`                          |

---

## Google OAuth Setup

1. Go to [Google Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com)
2. Create a project → Enable **Google+ API**
3. Credentials → OAuth 2.0 Client ID
4. Add `http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/google/callback` to Authorized redirect URIs
5. Copy `Client ID` and `Client Secret` to `.env`

## Cloudinary Setup

1. Sign up at [cloudinary.com](https://cloudinary.com)
2. Dashboard → Copy `Cloud Name`, `API Key`, `API Secret`
3. Add to `.env`
